epub2pdf (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * EPUB to PDF conversion with comprehensive CSS fixes.
  * Automatic book publisher detection (Manning, Wiley, Rheinwerk, etc.).
  * Support for single file and batch directory conversion.
  * Auto-generated Table of Contents with page numbers.
  * Figure centering, math sizing, table formatting recovery.

